'''凱西·穆里根'''（{{lang-en|Casey B. Mulligan}}）是美國經濟學家、[[芝加哥大学|芝加哥大学]][[经济学|经济学]]教授<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|last=|first=|date=|title=CV|url=http://legacy.iza.org/en/webcontent/personnel/vitae/321_cv.pdf|accessdate=2020-12-10|archive-date=2020-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200630091036/http://legacy.iza.org/en/webcontent/personnel/vitae/321_cv.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2018年9月至2019年8月期間擔任白宫[[经济顾问委员会|经济顾问委员会]]首席经济学家。<ref>{{Cite news|last1=Tankersley|first1=Jim|last2=Haberman|first2=Maggie|last3=Rabin|first3=Roni Caryn|date=2020-03-23|title=Trump Considers Reopening Economy, Over Health Experts' Objections|language=en|work=The New York Times|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/03/23/business/trump-coronavirus-economy.html|access-date=2020-06-27|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2020-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206015128/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/03/23/business/trump-coronavirus-economy.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Casey Mulligan Named Chief Economist for the Council of Economic Advisers | The University of Chicago Division of the Social Sciences|url=https://socialsciences.uchicago.edu/news/casey-mulligan-named-chief-economist-council-economic-advisers|access-date=2020-06-27|website=socialsciences.uchicago.edu|archive-date=2020-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200627222704/https://socialsciences.uchicago.edu/news/casey-mulligan-named-chief-economist-council-economic-advisers|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2020-01-13|title=Trump's Vast Deregulatory Landscape Goes Unnoticed by the Experts|url=https://economics21.org/trump-deregulation-unnoticed-experts|access-date=2020-06-27|website=Economics21|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201219182458/https://economics21.org/trump-deregulation-unnoticed-experts|dead-url=no}}</ref>

穆里根的主要研究领域是税收、监管、社会保险、政府行为等“[[公共经济学|公共经济学]]”。作为典型的[[芝加哥經濟學派|芝加哥学派]]经济学家，他主张「去监管」、缩减被认为会打击就业积极性的社会福利项目，也曾是反对“[[患者保护与平价医疗法案|奥巴马医保]]”的权威之一。在经济理念上与[[唐納·川普|唐納·川普]]颇为投契的穆里根於2018年正式投身特朗普政府，任白宫经济顾问委员会首席经济学家，直到2019年中。<ref name=voa>{{Cite news |url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/casey-mulligan-on-his-new-book/5691731.html |title=“我所看到的白宫跟外界谈论的一点都不一样” 专访特朗普总统前经济顾问穆里根 |publisher=VOA |date=2020-12-09 |accessdate=2020-12-10 |archive-date=2020-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212093833/https://www.voachinese.com/a/casey-mulligan-on-his-new-book/5691731.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2020年，穆里根将他在白宫的工作经歷写成了一本回忆录《你被雇用了：一位平民主义总统未被讲述的成功与失败》（''-{You’re Hired: Untold Successes and Failures of a Populist President}-''）。穆里根在书中描繪特朗普治下的白宮為有序、高效、目标坚定、成果丰硕，而特朗普本人则是一个“为人民代言”的“实验者”。穆里根也在書中驳斥了许多外界对于白宫的批评，还通过第一视角为特朗普本人所遭受的质疑辩护。<ref name=voa/>

